snippet.title: Official Trailer | Sally's Salon - Beauty Secrets
snippet.description:
Looking for a new hairdo? Want to get your nails done? Need some make up? There's no better place in Snuggford than Sally’s Salon! ▶︎▶︎▶︎ Play now: http://m.onelink.me/12ce44da

Your favorite beautician Sally returns to beautify women across the globe while searching for her long lost love. Join this hair-curling time management adventure now!
